title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Lockheed SR-71 blackbird - version 1.0
description:
In this video we will look at the Lockhead SR-71 "blackbird" which has been released as a beta. The aircraft is still under development and although the flying works there is still a lot of work to do. We will look at the exterior and interior and after this we try to taxi and take off.

If you also want to give this aircraft a try download your own copy from:
https://flightsim.to/file/21801/lockheed-sr-71-blackbird
